## API Request

All requests should be send to api.php file with parameters as explained Below. 
Response type is json


### Get Favorite Images

action : favorites_get


### Get Random Images

action : get_random

### Favorite an image

action : favorite_it
img_data : {
                thumb :  'VAL'  //thumbnail URL
                url : 'VAL'        // Image URL
                description : 'VAL'  // Image Description
}

### Delete Favorite Image

action : favorite_del
id : 'ID'  // Image ID

## Edit Favorite Image 

action: favorite_edit
img_data : {
            id : 'ID' // Image ID
            description : 'VAL' // Image Description
}
